OL,3,CCould plans for Guernsey's new sixth
OL,4,Cform centre be rehashed?
OL,6,FWords by ITV Channel reporter Matthew
OL,7,FLeach
OL,9,FTime and time again, we're told that
OL,10,Fone States Assembly can't bind its
OL,11,Fsuccessor to a decision.
OL,13,FOne president's plan can be dumped for
OL,14,Fanother, and this becomes ever more
OL,15,Fobvious when we revisit the proposals
OL,16,Ffor sixth form education in Guernsey.
OL,18,FThe state school sector is enjoying a
OL,19,Fmoment of stability, after several
OL,20,Fyears of false starts and confusion.
