OL,3,CCould plans for Guernsey's new sixth
OL,4,Cform centre be rehashed?
OL,6,FThis calmness comes courtesy of the
OL,7,Flast Education, Sport and Culture
OL,8,FCommittee (ESC), which managed to get
OL,9,Fpoliticians to agree to its plans for
OL,10,Fa new post-16 campus at Les Ozouets.
OL,12,FSixth-form students have been
OL,13,Ftemporarily sent to the old La Mare de
OL,14,FCarteret School, Les Varendes has
OL,15,Fbecome a fully fledged 11-16 school
OL,16,Fand everyone seems to be just getting
OL,17,Fon with it, while patiently waiting
OL,18,Ffor the campus to be built.
OL,20,FHowever, budget restraints saw the
OL,21,Ffull plans split into two phases.
