OL,3,CCould plans for Guernsey's new sixth
OL,4,Cform centre be rehashed?
OL,6,FWhile #88 million was ringfenced for
OL,7,Fthe Guernsey Institute and the
OL,8,Ffoundations of a sixth form centre,
OL,9,Fmoney for the second phase, building
OL,10,Fthe sixth form itself, was never
OL,11,Fapproved.
OL,13,FI expect the hope was that with the
OL,14,Ffoundations, this term's politicians
OL,15,Fwould be forced to find the money and
OL,16,Fbuild the rest of the sixth form
OL,17,Fcentre - but they don't have to.
