OL,3,CCould plans for Guernsey's new sixth
OL,4,Cform centre be rehashed?
OL,6,FWhile still getting his feet under the
OL,7,Ftable, the new President of ESC has
OL,8,Fsomewhat stated the obvious, which is
OL,9,Fthat with Guernsey's finances getting
OL,10,Fever tighter, the committee would be
OL,11,Fremiss not to assess all options
OL,12,Fbefore asking for more money.
OL,14,FDeputy Paul Montague told me: "The
OL,15,Fcurrent resolution with the States
OL,16,Findicates that a sixth form centre and
OL,17,Fa sports facility should be built on
OL,18,Fthe Les Ozouets Campus as part of
OL,19,Fphase two.
