OL,3,CCould plans for Guernsey's new sixth
OL,4,Cform centre be rehashed?
OL,6,F"That's still the plan. But of course,
OL,7,Fbearing in mind everything going on in
OL,8,Fthe island with funding and
OL,9,Fdemographics, we would be foolish not
OL,10,Fto look at other options.
OL,12,F"But we'll do so in a really
OL,13,Fmethodical, careful and evidence-based
OL,14,Fway."
OL,16,FSo while this opens the door to
OL,17,Falternatives, the education unions
OL,18,Fhave reiterated their support for the
OL,19,Fplan as it stands.
